<plot>Meet Homer J. Doyle, a pathetic old man whose meaningless life has slipped away. He's the night clerk, at a hotel for women from days gone by. Enter Edward Lambert, a likable young man, whose innocent search for his sister turns into a dubious mission. "Of Dreams and Glory" is a short film, suspense thriller that will make you think, "Be careful what you wish for".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?407479</url></doc>
